            | makes for a personalized shopping experience
          form#login-form.login-signup(action='')
            input#login-username.login(type='text' name='login-username' data-login='username' placeholder='USERNAME' required='')
            input#login-password.login(type='password' name='login-password' data-login='password' placeholder='PASSWORD' required='')
            h3#login-error-message.hidden(style='color: red; font-size: 18px')
              | We do not recognize your sign-in information. Please try again
